    "description": "Cardiff meets Kolkata with this aromatic twist on the classic Welsh rarebit. You'll top a toasted naan with a cheesy sauce packed with fragrant South Asian spices. Pop it under the grill to bubble until golden before serving up with pomegranate salad and roast potatoes.",
